, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; ">你对我说的</span><br style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; " />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; ">那些话</span><br style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; " />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; ">我摸不到</span><br style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; " />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; ">心却仿佛轻轻飘起</span><br style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; " />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; ">再飘落</span><br style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; " />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; ">又再飘起</span><br style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; " />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; ">&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; " />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; ">我试图摸摸你的心</span><br style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; " />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; ">可我摸不到</span><br style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; " />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; ">然后</span><br style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; " />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; line-height: 24.44444465637207px; ">我轻轻地呼唤你</span></p>\r\n', 44, 1385129697, 0, '七堇年', 1385632109, '', '我摸不到的，却可以用耳朵去倾听，用眼镜去观察，用心去体会。他们不是都说，眼睛看不到的人听觉非常的灵敏。虽然看不见，但是却可以听到别人听不到的声音。就像去展览馆看展览，隔着玻璃摸不到更加珍贵', '心情，摸不到', './up/cover/cover_1385129697_12.jpg'),
(23, 1, 263, '邂逅那些曾经最美的时光', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	/</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	于<a href="http://suiyue.sanwen8.cn/" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">岁月</a>深处</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	我看见一抹抹萧瑟在季节的枝头摇曳</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	于是，很多怀想便那一刻</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	从心底缓缓升起</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	左右着思绪为此迷惑</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	/</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	流年的<a href="http://cengjing.sanwen8.cn/" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">过往</a></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	总是在心底最脆弱的<a href="http://shijian.sanwen8.cn/" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">时候</a>占据心房</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	经年的风霜</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	也总是如期而至</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	将这个季节的冷意加重</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	/</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	泛白的光阴</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	唤起思绪千丝万缕</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	而<a href="http://huiyi.sanwen8.cn/" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">记忆</a>深处的那抹影子</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	在视线的距离里</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	渐渐变得清晰可亲</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	/</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	或许，一程<a href="http://shijian.sanwen8.cn/" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">时光</a></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	就是一段光阴</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	一程<a href="http://xinqingbuhao.sanwen8.cn/" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">心情</a></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	就有一段<a href="http://www.sanwen.net/tonghua.html" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">故事</a></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	但无论<a href="http://shijian.sanwen8.cn/" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">时间</a>怎么改变</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	也改变不了最初的风景</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	/</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	<a href="http://cengjing.sanwen8.cn/" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">曾经</a>，是多么美丽</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	总记得那一场紫色的烟<a href="http://xiayu.sanwen8.cn/" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">雨</a>里</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	还残留着当初的痕迹</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	还有，这一抹抹时光里</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	总有丝丝温柔的气息</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	在我的眉间轻吻着旧时的暖意</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	/</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	念，一缕缕泛起</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	在我温婉的情怀中</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	我将思绪转化成最初的模样</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	站立在最深的红尘里</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	再一次将过往刻进记忆</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	/</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	如水岁月</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	很多走过都已被埋没</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	而<a href="http://xinling.sanwen8.cn/" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">心灵</a>深处</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	依然只想做那个温柔的人儿</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 28px; ">\r\n	去邂逅曾经那段最<a href="http://www.sanwen8.cn/" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-decoration: none; " target="_blank">美的</a>时光</p>\r\n', 29, 1385397062, 0, '渠开源', 1385632094, '', '最美的时光总是让人怀念！', '邂逅，时光', './up/cover/cover_1385397062_5128.jpg'),
(24, 2, 273, '阳光暖洋洋的', '<p>\r\n	<span style="color:#ff0000;"><span style="font-size: 16px; ">天气晴朗，快出去晒晒吧！！！<img alt="cheeky" height="20" src="http://localhost/togetherwork/togetherwork/assets/ec317112/ckeditor/plugins/smiley/images/tounge_smile.gif" title="cheeky" width="20" /></span></span></p>\r\n', 304, 1385443084, 0, '四只奥特曼', 1385633476, '', 'sunshine', '晒太阳', './up/cover/cover_1385443084_2864.jpg');
